# ============================================
# ðŸ”‘ KEY MATCHING GUIDE
# ============================================
# These keys MUST have the same value:
#
# 1. Internal API Authentication:
#    - SHIPPER_API_KEY
#    - NEXT_PUBLIC_SHIPPER_API_KEY
#    â†’ Generate once with: openssl rand -hex 32
#
# 2. Cloudflare Worker Authentication:
#    - WORKER_API_KEY (in Railway/backend .env)
#    - API_KEY (in Cloudflare Worker secret)
#    â†’ Generate once with: openssl rand -hex 32
#    â†’ Set in worker: wrangler secret put API_KEY
#
# 3. These are DIFFERENT and UNIQUE:
#    - NEXTAUTH_SECRET (for NextAuth.js)
#    - SHIPPER_API_KEY (for internal API)
#    - WORKER_API_KEY (for Cloudflare Worker)
#    - DEPLOYMENT_PLANE_API_KEY (for deployment plane)
#
# ============================================
# QUICK SETUP COMMANDS
# ============================================
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Generate secrets:
#    NEXTAUTH_SECRET: openssl rand -base64 32
#    SHIPPER_API_KEY: openssl rand -hex 32
#    WORKER_API_KEY: openssl rand -hex 32
#    DEPLOYMENT_PLANE_API_KEY: openssl rand -hex 32
# 3. Fill in your API keys and credentials
# 4. Run: pnpm db:generate
# 5. Run: pnpm db:migrate:dev
# 6. Run: pnpm dev
#
# ============================================
# PRODUCTION DEPLOYMENT
# ============================================
# For Railway/production, update these URLs:
# - NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL="https://api.shipper.now"
# - WEB_APP_URL="https://app.shipper.now"
# - NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL="https://app.shipper.now"
# - DEPLOYMENT_PLANE_URL="https://deploy.shipper.now"
